Let $G$ be a group, suppose we have a family of normal subgroups
`$N_{i}\normalSubgroup G$` for `$i\in I$`. We have the induced morphism
`$\varphi\colon G\to\prod_{i\in I}G/N_{i}$` induced by the canonical
